# === Fallen Log ===
# Cylinder rotated 90deg around X-axis so it lies along Z.
# With ra=90 rx=1: cylinder's long axis (Y) tips to point in Z direction.
# Radius in Y = original sx/2 = 0.3, so center y=0.3 rests on ground.
(cylinder x=-6 y=0.3 z=-4 sx=0.6 sy=5 sz=0.6 ra=90 rx=1 ry=0 rz=0 mat='wood_04')
